lead_paragraph: The Marlins walked half a block alongside a hearse carrying their ace away from Marlins Park at the start of a funeral motorcade Wednesday, and then peeled away with watery eyes to go back inside and play a game.

headline.print_headline: Miami Leads Fernandez From Marlins Park; Mets Win 5-2
